productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Allean has one of these. She works as a sky diver and she says it looks weedy.
The box this comes in is 3 meter by 5 foot and weights 11 kilogram.
My co-worker Erick has one of these. He says it looks fluffy.
This Refined Granite Shoes works so well. It imperfectly improves my baseball by a lot.
